data.description: Welcome to your new haven at 1210 Martins Chapel Ln! Nestled in the heart of Lawrenceville, this 3-sided brick, 1.5 story ranch style home exudes warmth and comfort - 4 Bedrooms & 3.5 Bathrooms – Professionally Landscaped Front Yard - Spacious Driveway and extended Concrete Parking Pad – Foyer Entry - Open Concept Great Room with high Vaulted Ceiling and a gas starting Fireplace - Formal Dining Room with Wainscoting & Crown Moulding – Split Bedroom Plan with 2-Secondary Bedrooms with a Jack & Jill shared full Bathroom and Primary Suite on Main – Oversized Primary Bedroom with a Double Tray Ceiling – Primary Bathroom with Double Sink Vanity, Separate Shower, Jetted Tub, Water Closet and Spacious Walk-in Closet – Oversized Half Bathroom and Laundry Room on Main - Upgraded Kitchen with Caramel-colored  Cabinetry, ample storage, Kitchen Peninsula/Breakfast Bar and Stainless Steel Appliances – Breakfast Area featuring a Built-in Office Nook – Massive 4th Bedroom with Walk-in Closet, 3rd Full Bathroom, and accessible Attic on private Upper Level (perfect for multi-generational living (teenage or in-law suite), playroom, home office, or media room - Outdoor Oasis with a Screened in Back Patio with Panoramic Views to the Backyard, Hot Tub (included), stained Bead Board Ceiling, and Ceiling Fan - Generous backyard with lush greenery – Wood, Carpet & Tile flooring throughout - Window Blinds and Weed Control Service [for ROY] Included - HVAC System last serviced February 2024 - Gas Water Heater replaced 2021 -  Roof replaced 2017 - Close Proximity to Restaurants, Shops and Highway 316 – Don’t miss out on this meticulously cared for home!
